                    <p>

                        Homii’s Referral Incentive Program is an exciting opportunity for you to earn cash by referring Contractors to our site. It’s a small way for us to thank you for helping us grow our business!

                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Whenever someone signs up on Homii using your Referral link, you get 10% of their first year’s membership fees. You can earn up to 20% of all successful referrals after a certain number has been reached.  Below, we lay out the compensation breakdown.

                    </p>

                    @*<h1>
                        Refer Contractors & Earn Money
                    </h1>
                    <p>
                        Everybody knows somebody, so why not turn those connections into money? With Homii you can earn extra money with no work. Refer contractors and earn 10% of every sale.
                    </p>
                    <h1>
                        It can’t get any easier than this!
                    </h1>
                    <p>
                        When a contractor(s) signs up to Homii through your referral, you will receive 10% of the overall sale(s). The benefit for a contractor to sign up using your link is simple; they receive an additional month of service for free!


                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I.e., after you send your referrals, if one contractor signs up for an annual $3,000 membership, you make $300.

                    </p>*@

                    <div class="bg-white mt-4">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 text-center m-auto">
                                <div class="inner-incentive-box">
                                    <h2>Share Your Invitation Link</h2>
                                    <div id="shareIconsCountInside" class="cstm"></div>
                                    @*<div class="social-links">
                            <a href="javascript:;"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
                            <a href="javascript:;"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
                            <a href="javascript:;"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
                            <a href="javascript:;"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                        </div>*@
                                    @*<p>Share Your Referral Code To Earn $$</p>*@
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-7 m-auto">
                                            <form class="row">
                                                <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 pr-0">
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-inc mb-2" id="ReferCode" onblur="if(this.value == '') { this.value='Refer Code'}" onfocus="if (this.value == 'Refer Code') {this.value=''}" value="Refer Code" autocomplete="off">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12">
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-custom" onclick="CopyCode()">Copy url</button>
                                                </div>
                                            </form>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row_incntv_bx">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="inner-incentive-box incentbox amounts">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 pr-0">
                                                <h2>Total Earned</h2>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                                                <p class="p-font-size" id="TotalEarnedAmount"></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="inner-incentive-box incentbox amounts">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 pr-0">
                                                <h2>Total Due</h2>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12">
                                                <p class="p-font-size" id="AmountDue"></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="req-payment">
